				\begin{document}$$ \% \,downregulation=(0.6912\cdot {e}^{0.0348\cdot kozak\_strength})\cdot (\frac{388.61}{67.3}\cdot {e}^{-1.753\cdot uORF\_length})$$\end{document}%downregulation=(0.6912⋅e0.0348⋅kozak_strength)⋅(388.6167.3⋅e−1.753⋅uORF_length)Based on results from ref. 1, the contributions of the individual uORFs of a transcript were added together to arrive at the combined score for the entire transcript. These calculations were performed on all transcripts present in ENSEMBL for the human genome (release GRCh38.p5).
